creator: rainer.jung@kippdata.de
text:
JkLogLevel warn is documented but not implemented. Unknown LogLevels will
default to trace, which is not what you expect when using "JkLogLevel warn".

I will attach a patch that

- adds the detection of warn inside jk_util parse_log_level
- Fixes a minor typo

Created attachment 13736
Add detection of JkLogLevel warn to jk_util parse_log_level.
